Bayonne.364 and 390 Van Duzer Street: Houses at 364 and 390 Van Duzer Street are two historic homes located at Stapleton, Staten Island, New York. Number 364 Van Duzer Street is a ​2 1⁄2-story, clapboard-covered house with a gable roof. It features a tetrastyle portico with 2-story, Doric order columns.
